Maxima glanced with a soft, barely noticible smile. "As you command, Hydras," 
as was near what she replied to Megatron several times in the past. Oh, how 
she loved how his mind worked. It never tired nor gave up. Always in control, 
one step or more ahead of the situation. 

The clone... she could deal with. A virus to destroy Rodimus & the others.. 
would be perfection.

She turned & made her way to the doorway. 

--part1_3f.1ed2907c.2c2bd316_boundary
